Brix/Ocoticz stood up for the blast, launchers aimed at the hunters. 
For a second they thought Bronco was coming back, but he was able to 
be subdued.

"Come on, enough of this!" Brix scanned Sub-space. No weapons 
left. "Let's go into the ship."

The three maxis and the three prisoners enter the Cybertronian Fire.
